en_243972_0	Major General M.A.A.D Sirinaga assumed office as the Director General Financial Management in a simple ceremony at his office at the Army Headquarters north wing on Friday (14).
en_243972_1	He succeeded Major General W.R Palihakkara who retired from the Army recently.
en_243972_2	Major General Sirinaga was the former Director General of the Directorate of Electrical and Mechanical Engineers before he was appointed to the new appointment.
en_243972_3	The new DGFM signed a formal document and signified the acceptance of the new appointment soon after the traditional oil lamp was lit by him.
